headline: Does Fifth Third Still Offer Value After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Rally?
summary: If you have been wondering whether Fifth Third Bancorp is still good value after its run in bank stocks, you are not alone. This article is here to break that down in plain English. The stock has climbed 5.8% over the last week and 10.2% over the past month, adding to a longer track record of gains with a 66.6% return over 3 years and 110.4% over 5 years.
